  "title": "Assistant Performance Pathways Coach (Single-Handed)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Report to: ILCA Head Coach</strong></p><ol><li>Assist the ILCA Head Coach in developing the Yearly Planning Instruments (YPI) for ILCA 4 and 6 National Training Squad (NTS) sailors</li><li>Assist the ILCA Head Coach in the conduct of weekly training sessions at the National Sailing Centre</li><li>Work with the other NTS coaches to facilitate the transition of sailors between squads and sailing classes</li><li>Assist the ILCA Head Coach and liaise with the sport scientists from the High Performance Sport Institute (HPSI) to realise the Performance Pathway’s 360 Performance Development Approach: <br />a.  Regular fitness testing <br />b.  Clear fitness training approach <br />c.  Education of high performance nutrition and sport psychology techniques</li><li>Assist the ILCA Head Coach at selected overseas events where needed and submit post-event reports where required</li><li>Work with colleagues to organise selection trials, events and activities</li></ol>",
